            &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Do you journal? Are you a writer working on your next script?<br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="color: orange; font-weight: bold; font-style: italic;">Journal</span> provides its users with the ability to prepare documents with backdrops of their choice. This service is currently free to the public.<br><br> Enjoy!<br><br><span style="font-style: italic">-Admin (Allyse D. Johnson)</span>
